Signif. codes:  0 ?***? 0.001 ?**? 0.01 ?*? 0.05 ?.? 0.1 ? ? 1

1) I find that hard to believe. So, I made a subset of my data and ran the model with the subset, and while all other values changed, the between-study variance was still 0. 

2) So, now I am questioning either my code and/or my dataset. 

